## Design System Summary (same base, applied to new sections)

### Colors

* **Primary:** Blue-600, Blue-700, Indigo-800
* **Success:** Green (good metrics, on-time answers)
* **Warning:** Yellow (pending & borderline metrics)
* **Danger:** Red (high delays, high denials)
* **Background:** Gray-50 (page), White (cards), Amber/Orange (spotlight)

### Typography

* **Hero Title / Masthead:** 4xlâ€“5xl, bold
* **Section Titles:** 2xl, bold (Impact Story, Fresh Answers, Key Metrics, etc.)
* **Stats Numbers:** 3xlâ€“4xl, bold
* **Story Titles:** 1.25â€“1.5rem, semi-bold
* **Body:** Base size, high line-height

### Components

* **Story Cards:** White/colored backgrounds, shadow, rounded corners, with:

  * Title
  * 2â€“6 line summary
  * Metadata (topic, dept, dates)
  * Primary link to RTI detail
* **Metric Cards:** as in original (white, border, large number + subtitle)
* **Tables:** Department Leaderboard, Activity feed
* **Badges:** Status indicators (Answered, Pending, Denied, In Appeal)
* **Progress Bars / Bars:** For department performance, answer rates, etc.

### Spacing

* **Page padding:** px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8
* **Vertical spacing:** py-8 between major sections
* **Card padding:** p-6
* **Grid gaps:** gap-4 to gap-6

### Scroll Narrative

* **Top:** Lead Impact Story + Fresh Answers + Important Unanswered + What People Are Asking
* **Middle:** Hero banner, high-level stats, department performance, insights, topic browse, recent activity, spotlight
* **Bottom:** Deeper metrics & supporting info (you can add more system charts below), then footer.

---

